com.vmware.esx.settings.clusters.configuration

Class ClusterCompliance

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.esx.settings.clusters.configuration.ClusterCompliance
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.vmware.vapi.bindings.StaticStructure, com.vmware.vapi.bindings.Structure, java.io.Serializable

    public final class ClusterCompliance
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, com.vmware.vapi.bindings.StaticStructure
    This ClusterCompliance class contains properties that describe the compliance result for each host in the cluster as well as overall cluster compliance status. This class was added in vSphere API 8.0.1.0.
